# How to get these values:
# 1. Go to https://discord.com/developers/applications
# 2. Create/select your bot application
# 3. Copy the Application ID as DASHBOARD_CLIENT_ID
# 4. Go to OAuth2 settings
# 5. Copy the Client Secret as DASHBOARD_CLIENT_SECRET
# 6. Add http://localhost:3000/auth/discord/callback as a redirect URI
# 7. Generate a random string for SESSION_SECRET